<div class="header-spacer"></div>
    <div class="detail-page-container">
        
        <h1 class="detail-title">思源黑体-简体中文</h1>
          
          <div class="detail-content-wrapper">
              
              <aside class="detail-sidebar">
                  <div class="font-nav">
                      <h3>字体导航</h3>
                      <ul>
                          <li><a href="#font-info" class="active">字体简介</a></li>
                          <li><a href="#font-preview">字体展示</a></li>
                          <li><a href="#license-info">授权说明</a></li>
                      </ul>
                  </div>
              </aside>
              
              <main class="font-main-content">
                  
                  <section id="font-info" class="detail-section">
                      <h2>字体简介</h2>
                      <p class="description-text">思源黑体 (Source Han Sans/Noto Sans CJK) 是 Adobe 与 Google 合作开发的一款字体家族，共包含 7 种字重 (UltraLight, Light, Normal, Regular, Medium, Bold 和 Heavy)。它旨在为中文、日文、韩文以及拉丁文提供统一、高质量的字体支持，是设计师和开发者的首选免费商用字体之一。</p>
                  </section>
                  
                  <section id="font-preview" class="detail-section">
                      <h2>字体展示</h2>
                      <div class="main-preview-container" style="text-align: center;">
                          <img src="images/detail-preview-02.jpg" alt="字体预览图" class="detail-preview-img" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
                      </div>
                  </section>
                  
                  <section id="license-info" class="detail-section">
                      <h2>版权说明</h2>
                      <p class="license-p">These lines are licensed under the <a href="#" target="_blank">Open Font License</a>.</p>
                      <p class="license-p">You can use them in your products & projects - print or digital, commercial or otherwise.</p>
                      <p class="license-p">This isn't legal advice, please consider consulting a lawyer and view the full license for all details.</p>
                      <div class="full-char-set">
                      </div>
                  </section>
                  
              </main>

              <aside class="detail-info-card">
                  <div class="info-card">
                      <h3>字体信息</h3>
                      <div class="info-item">
                          <span class="label">授权类型</span>
                          <span class="value">开源可商用 (OFL)</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info-item">
                          <span class="label">文件大小</span>
                          <span class="value">16.3MB</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info-item">
                          <span class="label">支持格式</span>
                          <span class="value">OTF, TTF</span>
                      </div>
                      <a href="https://pan.baidu.com/share/init?surl=3eYlyLJc-SfKmVeBr354Ng&pwd=ehy4" class="download-button" target="_blank">
                          <span class="download-icon">↓</span> 百度网盘
                      </a>
                      
                      <a href="https://pan.quark.cn/s/ba9a23e36516#/list/share" class="download-button quark-button" target="_blank">
